               <sense xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann" xml:id="Dmain"> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዐረቀ፡</foreign> <subc>I,1</subc> [vicina sunt <foreign xml:lang="he">עָרָה עוּר עָרַר</foreign>, quibus significatus <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
